{"tid":1751332,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"區選完咗要繼續光復香港","createTime":"2019-11-24T16:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:11:41.000Z","uid":2762,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4638fdbc14b1579b67f5f69bf617569ad4855514","tid":1751332,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:59:48.000Z","msg":"見到好多建制垃圾被踢走當然開心<br />\n但呢個唔係我哋最終目標<br />\n唔好被一場小勝蒙蔽我哋嘅初衷<br />\n我地要嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n呢場區選小小嘅蠟燭仔係唔夠架照個香港<br />\n<br />\n香港人，報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfff19e4105b3d2bf6ca860efa5aab322992491","tid":1751332,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7aca4145071fdc0d6000b44ba2d1704d276e98bb","tid":1751332,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"提提大家"},{"pid":"2249cfbf0ab095b04713aa49c659dd1c2b5a9c87","tid":1751332,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:02:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db256f1499092aa2feab9847700facd8da038d8f","tid":1751332,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2c60e063309a840e85c00df740bbe7dbd588b00","tid":1751332,"uid":23023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"推 唔好因為區選收復失地而自滿<br />\n一路要做既始終都係要做"},{"pid":"d81ccce5f56c6004a7cb2f5725b43d737b91b2c6","tid":1751332,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc3c59b0b79af983cc3be2ccdfc76991d275f878","tid":1751332,"uid":109115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1a7f37fccf54803bb73c48d95664cad6c69506","tid":1751332,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［請廣傳］<br />\n和理非目前可以做到嘅事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">理大仲有幾十個留守者，佢哋每一分每一秒都承受極大心理壓力，仲有周梓樂、陳彥霖以及眾義士之死，有待昭雪，請大家快啲去投票，我地絕對唔可以辜負佢地，以下係和理非目前可以做到嘅事，香港重光之路永遠都需要大家和勇合一嘅團結，五大訴求，缺一不可！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一.）強烈建議香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">即時停止再月捐所有喺今次革命奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織</span>，將啲錢用喺更加有用嘅地方上面，例如揸車接放學嘅油費、飯券、法庭訟費、醫療開支、FA嘅物資費用等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織例子：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: gold;\">宣明會</span><br />\n（2018善款超過9.1億）：有巴絲post CUT捐回覆，「oh好遺憾」<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">無國界醫生</span><br />\n（2017總收入超5億）：有巴絲post非新聞稿答覆，達哥式回應（一直有mon住關注情況，屌你你mon到香港淪陷埋先出手不如）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（無恥界醫生條熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut）</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">樂施會</span><br />\n（2017總收入超2.5億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: gold;\">奧比斯香港</span><br />\n（2018年總收入超2.1億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: gold;\">UNICEF HK</span><br />\n（2017年總收入超1.7億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: gold;\">Save the Children</span><br />\n （2017年總收入超1.6億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n7. <span style=\"color: gold;\">香港紅十字會</span><br />\n（2017/18年總收入超1.4億）：18/8出咗份聲明，借世界人道主義日輕輕帶過呼籲各方克制，過去兩個多月動員逾800人次做電話熱線加現場支援<a href=\"https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redcross.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fpress_room%2Fpress_release_2019%2F201908182.html&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=fb89e5ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html</a><br />\n8. <span style=\"color: gold;\">國際培幼會</span><br />\n（2017年總收入近8000萬）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二.）本地文宣上，各區連儂牆近日被大肆清拆，各位香港人可以喺朝早人多時份重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三.）持續喺國際文宣上着力（Twitter, FB, IG），呼籲國際社會支持香港示威者五大訴求，順便將黑警惡行/ 中共建政70年嚟種種歷史惡行公諸於世"},{"pid":"3d8797c0ec48f54a8723b8861cfca5fdfbb79970","tid":1751332,"uid":237295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"ba370db3c4939c9a5924a22fdd8ab7b13e36b14e","tid":1751332,"uid":318349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"880134a7249e1c102dede66126e4ad311d85d518","tid":1751332,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4638fdbc14b1579b67f5f69bf617569ad4855514","tid":1751332,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:59:48.000Z","msg":"見到好多建制垃圾被踢走當然開心<br />\n但呢個唔係我哋最終目標<br />\n唔好被一場小勝蒙蔽我哋嘅初衷<br />\n我地要嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n呢場區選小小嘅蠟燭仔係唔夠架照個香港<br />\n<br />\n香港人，報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"香港人記住，落實五大訴求先係贏晒！"},{"pid":"5219c8971d3ab6645af7c25b402d5e1131febfda","tid":1751332,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"贏選舉只係光復嘅第一步<br />\n運動唔可以停<br />\nKeep 住個勢好快可以煲低見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5190577af481e6f6ca32bbd38b6ada838c8f640","tid":1751332,"uid":72863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"第一步我覺得要瘋狂文宣，連儂牆<br />\n第二步叫民陣申請遊行，無不反對就再諗方法<br />\n第三步我地諗立法會選舉"},{"pid":"1473bcda63dc6b1b293adbbc0bc364fee7a21a14","tid":1751332,"uid":33903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:04:31.000Z","msg":"當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi